<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Statue of Unity - India's Pride</title>
    <style>
        /* Classical CSS styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Garamond', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #8B4513;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #8B4513;
            font-size: 2.8em;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .monument-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border: 5px solid #D2B48C;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .section {
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #FAF0E6;
            border-left: 4px solid #CD853F;
        }

        .facts-list {
            columns: 2;
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .facts-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #D2B48C;
        }

        .quote {
            font-style: italic;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            color: #696969;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            
            .facts-list {
                columns: 1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>The Statue of Unity</h1>
            <h3>World's Tallest Statue</h3>
        </div>

        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/73/Statue_of_Unity.jpg" 
             alt="Statue of Unity" 
             class="monument-image">

        <div class="section">
            <h2>About the Monument</h2>
            <p>Standing tall at 182 meters (597 feet), the Statue of Unity is a tribute to Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel, India's first Deputy Prime Minister and the 'Iron Man of India'. Located in Gujarat, this engineering marvel was inaugurated on October 31, 2018.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <ul class="facts-list">
                <li>🗿 Height: 182 meters (597 feet)</li>
                <li>📍 Location: Sadhu Bet Island, Narmada District</li>
                <li>⚒ Construction Time: 42 months</li>
                <li>👷 Architects: Ram V. Sutar and Michael Graves</li>
                <li>📅 Inauguration Date: 31 October 2018</li>
                <li>🌍 Symbol: National Unity and Integrity</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="quote">
            "This statue will remind the world of India's engineering and technical capabilities"<br>
            - Narendra Modi
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Visitor Information</h2>
            <dl>
                <dt>🕒 Opening Hours:</dt>
                <dd>7:00 AM - 6:00 PM (Tuesday-Sunday)</dd>
                
                <dt>🎟 Entry Fee:</dt>
                <dd>₹ 150 for adults | ₹ 90 for children</dd>
                
                <dt>🚗 Parking:</dt>
                <dd>Available at base location</dd>
            </dl>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>